<bibRefCitation author="Nielson, M. W." box="[550,758,1251,1275]" pageId="75" pageNumber="74" pagination="137 - 139" refId="ref87553" refString="Nielson, M. W. 1986. New Oriental genus of leafhoppers in the tribe Coelidiini with descriptions of new species (Homoptera: Cicadellidae: Coelidiini). Great Basin Naturalist 46 (1): 137 - 139." type="journal article" year="1986">Nielson 1986:172</bibRefCitation>
